{"lemma":"مَعْقُول","slug":"مَعْقُول","root":"ع.ق.ل","root_slug":"ع-ق-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ق-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30001"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"seized by the intellect, comprehended, conceived"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"reasonable, logical, plausible, credible, sensible"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"comprehensible, intelligible, understandable"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wise"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"considerate"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"bound, held, restricted"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"comprehension, understanding"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of عَقَلَ (ʕaqala, “to be reasonable, to understand”), from the root ع ق ل (ʕ q l); compare عَقْل (ʕaql, “reason, intelligence”)."},"ipa":["/maʕ.quːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30001","headword_ar":"مَعْقُولٌ","root":"Eql","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[pass. part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqala","text_ar":"عَقَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in all its senses as a trans. verb. ―         -b2-  Hence it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intellectual,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perceived by the intellect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excogitated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus applied as an epithet to any branch of knowledge that is not necessarily"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoquwlN","text_ar":"مَنْقُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which means “ desumed, ” such as the science of the fundamentals of religion, and the like. ―         -b3-  Hence also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intelligible."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Approved by the intellect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reasonable."},{"kind":"text","text":"-A2-  It is also said to be an inf. n.]: see 1, latter half. ―         -b2-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqolN","text_ar":"عَقْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}